snippet.title: A Dark Place 2 Development: Sneak Peek 3 - New Mechanics and Tunnels Level Design Demo
snippet.description:
Please note that this is not a final production version of the game. Some things are subject to change throughout development.
The new 30-minute playable demo of the game is coming very soon.
Stay tuned!

Follow the game for more updates on A Dark Place 2:
https://gamejolt.com/games/ADP2/444700
Finished parts of the soundtrack can be found here:
https://soundcloud.com/mike-macson
